ave missed her chance this time around to representGreat Britainin two different sports at theOlympics, but as she returns to the world stage, the expectations are set high.Three years ago at Tokyo 2020she becameTeam GB's youngest-ever summer Olympian, and the team's youngest medallist.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9980470576905178, \"rank\": 0.0019531175828881374, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7121402451364071, \"rank\": 0.4042146104544004, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9411522793458147, \"rank\": 0.06175303235805187, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"summer Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her chance\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"Britainin\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"two different sports\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"2020she\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's youngest medallist\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are not many athleteswho qualify for the biggest event in their sport at just 12 years old, but that is what Brown achieved in May 2021, and the expectation has only grown since then.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athleteswho\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest event\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectation\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 15, Brown has over a million Instagram followers, more than 2 million on TikTok, and her and brother Ocean's combined YouTube channel has over 300,000 subscribers.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.171040215184084e-31, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9998495745519638, \"rank\": 0.00015044807935404137, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"over a million Instagram followers\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"over 300,000 subscribers\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also has her own Barbie doll.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"score\": 0.9999999976714662, \"rank