rown became the youngest-ever Nike-sponsored athlete in the world, having first stepped onto a board when she was just three and became a professional athlete at 10.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an 11-year-old Brown\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngest-ever Nike-sponsored athlete\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a board\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional athlete\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown could have represented Japan, but chose the country of her father's birth, at one point saying the decision was because of the British Skateboarding Association's more relaxed approach.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8082114368441692, \"rank\": 0.2067031072345126, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"score\": 0.999999606806873, \"rank\": 3.931932655998511e-07, \"text\": \"Skateboarding\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"Japan\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"her father's birth\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she was chosen for the 2021 Games, Brown became the youngest British summer Olympian, breaking a record set by Margery Hinton, who was 13 and 43 days when she competed in the 1928 Games.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8082114368441692, \"rank\": 0.2067031072345126, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"summer Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margery_Hinton\", \"score\": 0.9999995691608565, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Margery Hinton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margery_Hinton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margery_Hinton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Games\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"a record\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"13 and 43 days\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1928 Games\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike many Olympians, Brown was already an internationally-known athlete when she travelled to Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7121402451364071, \"rank\": 0.4042146104544004, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many Olympians\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"an internationally-known athlete\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There, she won the bronze medal, after falling in her first two runs, she scored 56.47 in here final attempt.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"her first two runs\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"here final attempt\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an impressive year for the British youngster, who won the X Games gold medal in July 2021, and was awarded BBC Young Sports Personality of the year.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2129, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8082114368441692, \"rank\": 0.2067031072345126, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an impressive year\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the X Games gold medal\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"BBC Young Sports Personality\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown then retained her X Games title the following year.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"her X Games\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"the following year\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, she won gold at the World Skateboarding Championship, become Britain's first skateboarding world champion.\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2380, \"end\": 2387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9936423164630727, \"rank\": 0.006398117241808927, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Skateboarding Championship\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around she will be 15, and despite missing out on the surfing qualification, the weight of expectation will weigh heavily on her young shoulders.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the surfing qualification\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"her young shoulders\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not feel pressure, honestly, having done it in Tokyo already,\\\" she said just months before the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2637, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7121402451364071, \"rank\": 0.4042146104544004, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It just makes me want to show my new tricks even more.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my new tricks\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just exciting for me.\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Skating is really not about the medals.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Skating\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about the show you put on for everyone.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always just want to show my best, and the beautiful part of skateboarding.\\\"\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beautiful part\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is that enthusiasm that has seen the nation take her to their hearts, and those extra three years can only have added to her skillset.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enthusiasm\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"their hearts\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"those extra three years\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"her skillset\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite only just being old enough to have done her GCSE's, Brown has already launched a book called the Life-Changing Magic of Skateboarding, a part biography and part guide to the sport, and she does not seem fazed by any aspect of her lifestyle, even the numerous media events.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Certificate_of_Secondary_Education\", \"score\": 0.9999999989349817, \"rank\": 1.0650023570533729e-09, \"text\": \"GCSE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Certificate_of_Secondary_Education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Certificate_of_Secondary_Education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \